partnerDetails.about: Established in 1979, Ellies Group is the leading Southern African manufacturer, importer, wholesaler and distributor of quality lighting, electrical and electronic products and solutions, to both the residential and commercial sectors. We also supply aerial and satellite equipment, accessories and hardware. So whether you need to manage your power in your home or plug your business in and flip the switch, we can help you.
